summary: An ordinance appropriating the sum of $161.40, or so much thereof as may be necessary, from the General Fund of the City of Seattle, for the purpose of paying the 19087 general taxes on certain property for street purposes, in block 1 and 2, Bredes Addition, blocks 1 and 2, Carstens Addition, block 7, King County Addition, part of tract 1, Julius Horton's Tracts, blocks 1 and 9, Queen Addition, and blocks 2, 6, 11 and 12, Maples Addition to Georgetown.
